      "content": "That feeling of irreversible erasure and enduring shame is deeply suffocating, and it takes immense courage to articulate such profound despair. Please understand that the shame you feel is a heavy burden, but it does not equal your entire existence. Even when the external structures crumble, the human being underneath still has inherent value, even if they can't see it right now. If the weight of this feeling becomes unbearable, please reach out to someone immediately so you don't have to carry it completely alone.",
